name: PROLACTA® 80 FOR INFANT NUTRITION
description: PROLACTA® 80 FOR INFANT NUTRITION is used in infant milk formula, Prolacta® contributes to the healthy growth and development of babies and toddlers. Providing the right intake of amino acids is key to protein synthesis without overloading the organism. Thanks to scientific research on infant nutrition, infant formula composition has evolved, and infant formula protein content has been reduced. Prolacta®’s high content of alpha-lactalbumin and tryptophan permits a lower total protein content.
